{
  "translationLines": [
    {
      "lineNumber": 9481,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "ふざける風でも悪びれるでもなく、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Without joking or feeling guilty,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9482,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "サイアスはウスピラの目を見る。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Saias looked into Uspira's eyes."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9483,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "そのサイアスに、どこかばつが悪そうに",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "To that Saias, somewhat awkwardly,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9484,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "ウスピラは視線を逸らした。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Uspira turned her gaze away."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9485,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「……お節介、よ。サイアスは」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"...You're meddlesome, Saias.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9486,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「そうかもしれないが……ごめんな。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"That may be true... I'm sorry."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9487,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　でも、今は……行動しない事が、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "But right now... not taking action"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9488,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　何より愚かしいと思う」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "is the most foolish thing, I think.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9489,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「………………」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "................"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9490,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「こないだ、部下に告白されたんだ」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"The other day, a subordinate confessed to me.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9491,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「……それがなに？」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"...So what about that?\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9492,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "口にした響きに棘が混じっていた事を、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Internally, Uspira was surprised that"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9493,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "内心でウスピラは驚いていた。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "there was a sting mixed in his spoken tone."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9494,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「ま、断ったが。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Well, I refused him."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9495,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　……でも、正しいとは思った。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "But... I thought it was the right thing to do."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9496,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　こんな時代だ。躊躇してるヒマはない、ってね」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "In times like these, there's no time to hesitate.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9497,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「誰かのために……好きな相手と、生きるために。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"For someone... to live with the person you love."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9498,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　そう思う事は、きっと生き抜く力になる」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "To think that way surely becomes the strength to survive.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9499,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「誰かを、生かして……自分も、生きる。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"To keep someone alive... and to live yourself."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9500,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　そう思って、初めて誰かを守れるんだと、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Only by thinking that can you truly protect someone,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9501,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　俺は思うんだ」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "I believe.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9502,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "緩く握った手を開き、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Opening his loosely clenched hand,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9503,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "サイアスはウスピラに手をさしのべた。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Saias reached out his hand to Uspira."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9504,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「だから……一緒に生きよう、ウスピラ。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"So... let's live together, Uspira."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9505,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　お互いが、お互いを支えられるように」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "So that we can support each other.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9506,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「ん…………うん」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Mm... yeah.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9507,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "躊躇いがちに、ウスピラはその手を取った。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Hesitantly, Uspira took his hand."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9508,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「………………！　本当か！」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\".........! Is it really true!\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9509,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「えっ……！？」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Eh...?!!\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9510,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "表情が一転して明るくなったサイアスに、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Saias's expression suddenly brightened,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9511,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "ウスピラは驚いてその顔を見上げる。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "and Uspira looked up at him in surprise."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9512,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「はははは、やった！",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Hahaha, I did it!"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9513,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　やっとプロポーズ成功だ！　やったぞ！！」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Finally, the proposal succeeded! I did it!!\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9514,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "拳を突き上げて叫ぶサイアスを、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Saias raised his fist and shouted,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9515,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "ウスピラは慌てて押しとどめる。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "but Uspira hurriedly stopped him."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9516,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「ち、ちが……違う、違うわ、サイアス……！",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"N-no... that's not it, Saias...!"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9517,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　その、それは、な、仲間として、という……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Th-that, um, is as comrades...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9518,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「えっ？」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Eh?\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9519,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「………………」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "................"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9520,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「……………………そうなのか」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"...Is that so?\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9521,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「そ…………そうよ」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Y-yes, that's right.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9522,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「そうかーーーー……まいったな、また失敗か……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"I see... damn, failed again...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9523,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "がっくりと、サイアスは肩を落とした。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Saias sagged his shoulders in dejection."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9524,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "一転して、この世の終わりかという顔をする。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "He looked as if it were the end of the world."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9525,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「それは……その、だって、そんないきなり……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Well... but, that was so sudden...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9526,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「俺はいきなりじゃないつもりだったが……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"I didn't think it was sudden...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9527,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「それは……」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"That is...\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9528,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "いっそ哀れになるくらい、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Almost pitifully,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9529,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "サイアスは落胆している……ように見えた。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Saias seemed thoroughly disappointed."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9530,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「仕方ないな。じゃあ、せめてデートしないか。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"It can't be helped. Then, at least, shall we go on a date?"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9531,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　そのくらいはいいだろう」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "That much should be fine.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9532,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「っ……じゃあ、視察のついででいいなら」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"...Then, if it's just while on inspection, that's fine.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9533,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「よし！　もちろんいいぜ。君に渡したい物もある。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Alright! Of course that's fine. I also have something I want to give you."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9534,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "　楽しみにしていてくれ」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Look forward to it.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9535,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "あっさりと喜色満面になって頷いてから、",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "After cheerfully nodding,"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9536,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "サイアスは部隊指揮のために踵を返しかけた。",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "Saias started to turn on his heel to command the troops."
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9537,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「サイアス」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Saias.\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9538,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「ん？」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"Hmm?\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9539,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「…………貴方は……死なないで、ね」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"...You... won't die, okay?\""
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9540,
      "originalJapaneseLine": "「死なない。心中なんて真似も、しない」",
      "translatedEnglishLine": "\"I won't die. I won't do anything like a double suicide.\""
    }
  ]
}

